r.s: Binding for FANN (Fast Artificial Neural Network) Library
r.d: This package provides PHP binding for FANN (Fast Artificial Neural Network) Library
r.n: * New functional API supporting libfann version 2.1 and 2.2. * More than 140 new functions. * Many new algorithms and options for neural networks. * Incompatible with previous version (rewritten from scratch).
